name: colapso
description:
This piece is from the collection "descartável", which is a audiovisual project that I discarded bad feelings and turned it into something that could heal me. The project addresses mental health issues, self knowledge and it was a opportunity to me to study animation. This is the twelfth piece of the collection. 

Separated for #oBRjkt2 | #FORABOLSONARO
